data.description: This Gorgeous townhome has been updated and is move in ready!! The open floor plan is more than spacious with over 1525 sqft, 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Driveway has also been extended for 2 car parking. New flooring and trim recently installed along with freshly painted cabinets. Master bedroom with 2 large closets and a granite top double vanity in the bathroom.  The kitchen has granite countertops with bar top seating and all brand new matching appliances. Sliding glass door leads to the large backyard with an expansive patio and dog run along the side on the home. HOA covers water, sewer and front yard landscaping.
